Mouse bindings
---------------
On desktop or xclockbar:

- Right click: show application menu
- Middle click: show group menu
- Left click: show window menu
- Scroll: Change sound volume

Put the mouse on bottom left corner to see jgmenu.

Keyboard bindings
------------------
Bindings are cwm plus a few (see ``man cwm``)

M: Alt
C: Ctrl
S: Shift

- M-Left click: move window 
- M-Right click: resize window 
- M-p : spawn dmenu_run_i to start a command
- C-M-Return: spawn xterm
- C-M-m: maximize window 
- M-Tab: cycle windows
- M-g: Send focused window to another group
- M-Space: Cycle throught groups
- M-F4 or M-C-x: close window
- M-s : start dsch to search on the web
- M-x : start dfm
